SYNTAX:
&lt;cfmenu 
    bgcolor=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">HTML color value</i>&quot; 
    childStyle=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">CSS style specification</i>&quot; 
    font=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">HTML font family</i>&quot; 
    fontColor=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">HTML color value</i>&quot; 
    fontSize=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">Number of pixels</i>&quot; 
    menuStyle=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">CSS style specification</i>&quot; 
    name=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">string</i>&quot; 
    selectedFontColor=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">HTML color value</i>&quot; 
    selectedItemColor=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">HTML color value</i>&quot; 
    type=&quot;horizontal|vertical 
    width=&quot;<i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">Number of pixels</i>&quot;&gt; 
 
        <i xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">cfmenuitem tags</i> 
 
&lt;/cfmenu&gt;<br>The <samp class="codeph">cfmenu</samp> tag must have a body that contains at least one <samp class="codeph">cfmenuitem</samp> tag to define the menu items and an end <samp class="codeph">&lt;/cfmenu&gt;</samp> tag.<br><span class="notetitle">Note: </span>You can specify this tag’s attribute in an 
<samp class="codeph">attributeCollection</samp> attribute whose value is a structure. Specify the structure name in the 
<samp class="codeph">attributeCollection</samp> attribute and use the tag’s attribute name as structure key.<br>

EXAMPLE:
The following example creates a simple menu bar. When you click an entry in the bar, the browser displays the Adobe website page for the selected product. You can expand the ColdFusion item by clicking the icon, and then select an item to display a specific ColdFusion web page.<br>&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt; 
&lt;head&gt; 
&lt;/head&gt; 
&lt;body&gt; 
&lt;cfmenu name=&quot;menu&quot; type=&quot;horizontal&quot; fontsize=&quot;14&quot; bgcolor=&quot;##CCFFFF&quot;&gt; 
    &lt;cfmenuitem name=&quot;acrobat&quot; href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/acrobat&quot; display=&quot;Acrobat&quot;/&gt; 
    &lt;cfmenuitem name=&quot;aftereffects&quot; href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/aftereffects&quot;  
        display=&quot;After Effects&quot;/&gt; 
    &lt;!--- The ColdFusion menu item has a pop-up menu. ---&gt; 
    &lt;cfmenuitem name=&quot;coldfusion&quot; 
            href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/products/coldfusion&quot; display=&quot;ColdFusion&quot;&gt; 
        &lt;cfmenuitem name=&quot;buy&quot; 
            href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/products/coldfusion/buy/&quot; display=&quot;Buy&quot;/&gt; 
        &lt;cfmenuitem name=&quot;devcenter&quot; 
            href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/devnet/coldfusion/&quot; display=&quot;Developer Center&quot;/&gt; 
        &lt;cfmenuitem name=&quot;documentation&quot; 
            href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/support/documentation/en/coldfusion/&quot; 
                display=&quot;Documentation&quot;/&gt; 
        &lt;cfmenuitem name=&quot;support&quot; href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/support/coldfusion/&quot;  
            display=&quot;Support&quot;/&gt; 
    &lt;/cfmenuitem&gt; 
    &lt;cfmenuitem name=&quot;flex&quot; href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/flex&quot; display=&quot;Flex&quot;/&gt; 
&lt;/cfmenu&gt; 
&lt;/body&gt; 
&lt;/html&gt;<br>
